description: [``botocore``] This release adds support for 4GB/s / 160K PIOPS FSx for ONTAP file systems and 10GB/s / 350K PIOPS FSx for OpenZFS file systems (Single_AZ_2). For FSx for ONTAP, this also adds support for DP volumes, snapshot policy, copy tags to backups, and Multi-AZ route table updates.
